{"tid":1720493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【手足獻計】同越共一樣打遊擊戰","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T11:41:12.000Z","uid":44870,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48c0983ae8889cc4adc51917de7a9b576f606f8c","tid":1720493,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"香港多山，高樓，易Hide and surprise，所以啲狗永等收哂風先攻，同成日回防<br />\n越南多叢林，易Hide<br />\n一群人搞喺搞去，只會磨士氣，同令市民更反感<br />\n唔會突破，不進則退<br />\n反而，要搞重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋搞重點就係攻大學,其中一個原因係學生住嘅地方，學生地頭<br />\n我哋一樣，搞返佢哋地頭<br />\n獻世派議員屋企呀，狗宿呀，<br />\n佢哋依家就係唔擔心會有任何personal損失，所以夠膽咩都做！</span></span><br />\n要改變佢哋思維，要佢哋每步都要諗多次，驚一驚，士氣低落<br />\n<br />\nImagine 關節技：佢哋有social attachments就係佢哋嘅關節弱點<br />\n- credit FuckMinds"},{"pid":"972d0ea7bbab21c072791adce6fdc8935897a2b1","tid":1720493,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"周梓樂手足頭七<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1wBo4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1wBo4F.jpg&h=3452e01d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>他永遠停了在22歲。<br />\n你甘心他至今仍走得不明不白嗎？<br />\n他在天上也會安心嗎？</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suk2342.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsuk2342.png&h=07c123f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68ed38b2c984745f6ad49d7da5b953bee11c239b","tid":1720493,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"其實學越共整陷阱好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89016c76ea268d93547494d6eacbca25484aafde","tid":1720493,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"Thank you bro, 請支持我另一